    end

    MEM -->|"every 100 ticks"| BRIDGE
    BRIDGE -->|"SSH + JSON"| WATCHER
    WATCHER -->|"12 sections\nwith ETL"| UNITS
    WATCHER -->|"CDC\ndetection"| UE
